item.title: Getting Help
item.description: Welcome to the Open Cluster Management community! We want to hear from you. How you are using open-cluster-management? What we can do to make it better? To understand how the Open Cluster Management community is governed, visit the Community repo. Github Project Check out the project and consider contributing. You can pick up an issue to work on, or report a bug by creating a new issue here. When your code is ready to be reviewed, you can propose a pull request.
